  "texts": [
    "Therefore, the combination of image captioning technology and image classification tasks addresses the first challenge.",
    "CNNbased image classification models may struggle to learn sufficient discriminant features, leading to slower performance in recognizing image classes (Luo et al., 2018).",
    "When there are limited image data samples, leveraging the benefits of multi-task learning can effectively mitigate the performance decline caused by the small sample size.",
    "Multi-task learning aims to extract useful information from other tasks and apply it to the current task, leading to an improved model performance model (Ruder, 2017).",
    "Image caption generation technology can extract rich semantic features from images (Xian et al., 2022)."
  ],
